{"tid":1624990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日應該推和理非活動","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:06:17.000Z","uid":162909,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5163671bf9e8adcb7e241ea342f4e1344bc42f","tid":1624990,"uid":162909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:30:37.000Z","msg":"第一次開post<br />\n<br />\n頭先有巴打話依家政府將我地推向兩難嘅局面<br />\n<br />\n但唔代表大家今日乜都唔好做<br />\n<br />\n其實我地可以呢兩日不停蒙住面做和理非活動<br />\n<br />\n例如今日試下將文宣摺成紙飛機，然後大量飛入政總，營造反個和理非嘅形象俾國際睇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"8eb5160aa8c6ace9756d2961d3c778d905c59087","tid":1624990,"uid":162909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"自推10連！<br />\n<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"3f537d2973cd5c1e46bf11488ddef071fe034255","tid":1624990,"uid":162909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"自推10連！<br />\n<br />\n2/10"},{"pid":"27e85524ea72ae89a2017ab0a6cde2c59aafc47e","tid":1624990,"uid":162909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"自推10連！<br />\n<br />\n3/10"},{"pid":"84455b97075038c345c2ebfac9911daa57192157","tid":1624990,"uid":162909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"自推10連！<br />\n<br />\n4/10"},{"pid":"7d9e4fd1f1e6ea71abb24723abcd50fde1c43478","tid":1624990,"uid":257293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"其實裝修有好多種<br />\n點解唔裝修成連儂牆？<br />\n新聞出嘅圖可以贏到輿論同國際支持<br />\n又可以target警世呢啲紅底中資<br />\n佢哋要拆要清都要搞到一大輪<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33